long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get ready for an electrifying soccer experience with Big Head Soccer! Take control of a character with a giant head and even bigger ambitions in fast-paced 1v1 matches. Whether you're challenging friends or facing off against AI opponents, every match is packed with intense action. Use your head (literally) to score goals, defend your net, and dominate the pitch.

Why Install?
Fast-Paced Action: Enjoy quick, thrilling matches that are perfect for a burst of fun.
Simple Controls: Easy-to-learn controls make it accessible to players of all ages.
Multiplayer Mode: Compete against friends or players from around the world to prove your skills.
Unique Characters: Choose from a variety of quirky characters, each with their own distinct style.
Explore the menu at the top-left for more options, and use the rate and share icons at the bottom-right to enhance your gaming experience. Ready to score big? Let’s play! 🥅
